      <li style="margin-bottom: 0">
        <b>Unisexual</b>: Reproductive structure that is either functionally male or functionally female. In angiosperms this condition is also called<span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span><b>imperfect</b>, or<span class="Apple-converted-space">&#160;</span><b>incomplete</b>.
      </li>
    </ul>
