      <li>
        Field or Garden Peas - <i>R. leguminosarum bv. viciae</i>
      </li>
      <li>
        Crimson, Red, White and Alsike Clover - <i>R. leguminosarum bv. trifolii</i>
      </li>
      <li>
        Hairy Vetch, Fava Beans, Broad Beans - <i>R. leguminosarum bv. viciae </i>
      </li>
